1. Convert to TypeScript
$ yarn add --dev typescript @types/react @types/node

2. Add Apollo Micro Service
$ yarn add graphql apollo-server-micro

3. Add the micro module
$ yarn add micro

4. Add TypeGraphQL
@see https://typegraphql.com/docs/installation.html
$ yarn add reflect-metadata class-validator type-graphql

5. Syncronize the grqphql version in package.jons to v15.x.x
6. import "reflect-metadata" (api/graphql.ts);
7. Add to tsconfig
 {
  "emitDecoratorMetadata": true,
  "experimentalDecorators": true,
  "target": "es2018",
  "lib": ["esnext.asynciterable"]
 }